{"title":"军属的心愿","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1953,"month":7,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"军属的心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马爱群五月的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拂着麦梢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还没灌浆哩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足足有尺半高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“今年又是个丰收年”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民们欣喜相告。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说着的笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听着的也笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张二嫂赶集回来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边走一边盘算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么写信向他报告："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“去年十二成年景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃了穿了还剩了不少；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年麦子又要大丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活一年会比一年好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我参加了青年团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又上了夜校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个月认了三千字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不光会写信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还会看书报。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你啥也别想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只想怎着把仗打好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我啥也不盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只盼你寄回张立功喜报。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张二嫂越想越高兴，喜在心里，笑在眉梢。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}